OL,3,CHomes destroyed in fire 'by suspected
OL,4,Cfirework' on New Years Eve
OL,6,FA family home and neighbouring house
OL,7,Fwere destroyed after a suspected stray
OL,8,Ffirework ignited a fire on the night
OL,9,Fof New Years Eve.
OL,11,FKarolyn and Richard Ward had just
OL,12,Ffinished watching the New Years Eve
OL,13,Ffireworks on TV with their daughter
OL,14,Fwhen they saw smoke out of their
OL,15,Fwindow.
OL,17,FThe fire spread to the house so
OL,18,Fquickly that they had to escape out
OL,19,Ftheir window with nothing but the
OL,20,Fclothes on their backs.
