OL,4,Cfirework' on New Years Eve
OL,6,FRichard said: "Five minutes later and
OL,7,Fwe would've been in bed."
OL,9,FKarolyn added: "I dread to think what
OL,10,Fwould've happened because we wouldn't
OL,11,Fhave got out. I've never seen a fire
OL,12,Fspread so quick.
OL,14,F"I'm a wreck. You are just tearful all
OL,15,Fthe time. Our daughter was terrified
OL,16,Fto go to sleep last night."
OL,18,FThere was a lot of wind in the area on
OL,19,Fthe night and the fire service
OL,20,Fcurrently believe it is most likely
OL,21,Fthat a stray firework caused the blaze.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
