OL,4,Cfirework' on New Years Eve
OL,6,FIt had been the family's home for over
OL,7,Fa decade and all of their possessions
OL,8,Fwere lost.
OL,10,FRichard said: "I've got nothing left
OL,11,Fat all. My house is just a complete
OL,12,Fshell and it's unsafe.
OL,14,F"All of our wedding photos, baby
OL,15,Fphotos, drawings from school... all of
OL,16,Fthat was in the loft and it's all
OL,17,Fgone."
