OL,6,FThe fire service left the scene
OL,7,Finitially at 3am but returned a few
OL,8,Fhours later when the fire had
OL,9,Freignited.
OL,11,FWhen they first attended the scene
OL,12,Fthey reported minimal damage on the
OL,13,Fneighbouring house. But by their
OL,14,Fsecond visit both houses were severely
OL,15,Fdamaged.
OL,17,FJayden, who owns the neighbouring
OL,18,Fhouse, was away on the night.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
