OL,6,FHe said: "Everything is basically
OL,7,Fgone... my grandad's ashes and all my
OL,8,Fphotos.
OL,10,F"This was my first home. I got it when
OL,11,FI was 20 and I worked hard since I was
OL,12,F16 to save up and managed to get it on
OL,13,Fmy own. I did the kitchen and bathroom
OL,14,Fall by myself which I had never done
OL,15,Fbefore."
OL,17,FThe community has rallied together to
OL,18,Fsupport Jayden and the Ward family by
OL,19,Fgifting them hundreds of items.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
