OL,6,FSeparate fundraising pages were also
OL,7,Fset up to help them rebuild their
OL,8,Flives and have already raised
OL,9,Fthousands of pounds.
OL,11,FKarolyn said: "For this to happen you
OL,12,Fthink how silly are people are people
OL,13,Fto have been letting off fireworks on
OL,14,Fsuch a windy night in a weather
OL,15,Fwarning.
OL,17,F"But then we have had so much donated.
OL,18,FMy mum's house is full and my in-laws'
OL,19,Fhouse is full. We could never thank
OL,20,Fpeople enough ever."
